GUI DEPOSIT/WITHDRAW TAB

Test Case 1:
Requirement: There should be an error message printed in the textarea in the GUI if any textfield is empty.
Test Description: Created a test with empty first name text field.
Input Data: First Name:  , Last Name: p, Dob: 10/12/1999, Amount: 1000, Account Type: Checking
Expected Result : Warning:"All fields must be filled out to deposit/withdraw from an account." and also prints out "Missing data for depositing/withdrawing into/from an account." in textarea.

Test Case 2:
Requirement: There should be an error message printed in the textarea in the GUI if any accountType radiobutton is not selected.
Test Description: Created a test with no radio buttons selected in accountType
Input Data:  First Name: r, Last Name: p, Dob: 10/12/1999, Amount: 1000, Account Type:
Expected Result : Warning:"Please select an account Type" and also prints out "Missing data for depositing/withdrawing into/from an account." in textarea.

Test Case 3:
Requirement: There should be an error message printed in the textarea in the GUI when the amount entered isn't a valid amount
Test Description: Created a test with an invalid amount
Input Data: First Name: r, Last Name: p, Dob: 10/12/1999, Amount: a, Account Type: Checking
Expected Result : Prints out "Not a valid amount." in the GUI textarea.

